{
  "stem": "14897.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To get to Wilno-- by the way, W-I-L-N-O, in Polish-- it has different names depending on the language-- you have to pass through the part of Poland occupied by Russia.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- my mother, and I and an aunt and her son, we made it to a town called Bialystok in occupied Russia-- B-I-L-L-Y-S-T-O-K.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the same aunt, Zina Hurwicz, and her son's name is Henry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he's still alive and lives in California.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to pass an illegal border between Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were people who conducted us, of course, for money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got-- we traveled by lorry-- by, by truck-- and then we walked to some wealthy peasant's home on the German side.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father still stayed in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the problem was to get yourself transported and whatever money you had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you traveled with the money and somebody knew it, you were not likely to get anywhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we traveled first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my father was-- when we were already in Bialystok, my father tried to transport the money to Wilno.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the money made it and got to United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we got-- when the war ended, my father and I owned $8,000, which was at the time a considerable amount of money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, so here we are in this peasant's hut-- big hut.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then at night, we had to t-- to cross the River Bug, B-U-J, which was the border between Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we crossed it on little rowboats, got to the Russian side, walked to another peasant's home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we were there, the Russian soldiers came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And fortunately, one of them was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he started talking to my aunt in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
